<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Goblin Game Shop</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0a0a23; /* Dark blue for vaporwave goblin vibe */
            color: #fff;
        }
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 100vh;
            background-image: url('https://example.com/path_to_your_goblin_image.jpg'); /* REPLACE with your uploaded image URL */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        .nav {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .nav a {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .nav a:hover {
            color: #00ff00; /* Goblin green glow */
        }
        .clickable-area {
            position: absolute;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 5;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); /* Semi-transparent for testing; set to transparent in production */
            border: 1px dashed #fff; /* Dashed border for testing; remove later */
        }
        #table { /* Click for Shop - Position over the table in image */
            top: 60%; /* Adjust these based on your image */
            left: 35%;
            width: 150px;
            height: 120px;
        }
        #door { /* Click for Home - Position over the door */
            top: 40%;
            left: 55%;
            width: 100px;
            height: 200px;
        }
        #wardrobe { /* Click for Contact - Position over the wardrobe/shelf */
            top: 20%;
            left: 70%;
            width: 120px;
            height: 250px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgba(10, 10, 35, 0.8); /* Semi-transparent overlay for readability */
        }
        h1 {
            color: #00ff00; /* Green for goblin theme */
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="nav">
            <a href="#home">Home</a>
            <a href="#shop">Shop</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
        <div id="table" class="clickable-area" onclick="document.querySelector('#shop').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'});"></div>
        <div id="door" class="clickable-area" onclick="document.querySelector('#home').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'});"></div>
        <div id="wardrobe" class="clickable-area" onclick="document.querySelector('#contact').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'});"></div>
    </div>
    <section id="home" class="content">
        <h1>Welcome to Goblin Game Shop!</h1>
        <p>Step into our janky, colorful goblin hut for TCG battles, Warhammer skirmishes, and collectible chaos. We're scouting spots in Central NJ or Philly for your local gaming immersion—join the outmatched goblin soldiers in epic, irrational fun!</p>
    </section>
    <section id="shop" class="content">
        <h1>Shop Our Goblin Hoard</h1>
        <p>Browse Magic: The Gathering singles, Pokémon cards, Warhammer minis, and more. Out of stock? It's goblin science—painted different colors for luck! Syncing with TCGPlayer for e-commerce deals. [Embed Shopify products or TCG links here]</p>
    </section>
    <section id="contact" class="content">
        <h1>Contact the Goblin Clan</h1>
        <p>Got questions on store locations, events, or buying/selling TCGs? Email us at info@goblingameshop.com or drop by our future Philly/NJ spot for in-person trades.</p>
    </section>
    <script>
        // Prevent default for better UX if needed
        console.log('Goblin Hut Loaded - Ready for Battle!');
    </script>
</body>
</html>